data.description:
Discover your ideal home nestled in the beautiful Palm Coast, Florida. This charming single-family residence is the perfect blend of comfort and functionality, featuring three cozy bedrooms and one and a half modern bathrooms. Step inside to find a beautifully updated interior complete with sleek granite countertops and stainless appliances, ready for your culinary adventures.

The spacious layout flows effortlessly onto a large, private backyard oasis, shaded by majestic palm trees and surrounded by lush landscaping, offering a tranquil retreat on a generous 0.23-acre lot. The convenience of a one-car garage adds to the functionality of this home, providing ample storage and parking space.

Whether you're hosting family gatherings or simply enjoying Florida's delightful climate, this property strikes the ideal balance between peaceful living and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this haven your very own personal paradise.
